>对于 Guardians of the Galaxy(银河护卫队这个译名…)只想借用一句词来表达——“声光电俱佳”。<br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, tahoma, arial, simsun, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19.600000381469727px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 239);\"/>电影呈现的不仅是视觉盛宴，也是听觉盛宴，音乐盛宴。配乐很喜欢，还有那些熟悉且喜欢的歌，再播下去就要跟着唱出声了…真的以为只有星爵一个人想跳舞吗？其实自己也想(算不算丢人，汗)！这张原声绝对值得列入今年的收藏表！&nbsp;<br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, tahoma, arial, simsun, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19.600000381469727px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 239);\"/>他们绝不是常规的英雄，说二货也好，疯子也好，逗比也罢，但他们绝对是最萌的组合，最佳的搭档。不用过多表述所有人背负的过去，也不用刻意煽情，吵吵闹闹，用笑声一样可以撼动人心。他们就是活在当下的一群人，自由的人，“我就是我”便是他们的代言。<br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, tahoma, arial, simsun, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19.600000381469727px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 239);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, tahoma, arial, simsun, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19.600000381469727px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 239);\"/>怎么都感觉罗南的戏少了点…即使有个几乎认不出的造型，光听声音还是能辨的出佩佩…(好了，打住吧)<br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, tahoma, arial, simsun, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19.600000381469727px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 239);\"/>“树带熊”一出场周围的妹子就萌翻了，听到尖叫了哎，这是男神级待遇吧！其实这个团队哪只是不萌的？<br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, tahoma, arial, simsun, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19.600000381469727px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 239);\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, tahoma, arial, simsun, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19.600000381469727px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 239);\"/>为什么到最后，全场算上自己和同事只有六个人在等彩蛋？？？还有俩字幕没滚完就走人了…<br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, tahoma, arial, simsun, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-